    "long_instructions": "Combine random numbers with a loop to gather ingredients dynamically.\r\n\r\n## Do This: \r\n- Run the code to see how ingredients are gathered using dice rolls.\r\n- Modify the code to stop rolling once you have at least 15 ingredients.",
